==English==
===Adjective===
'''little'''

#Small
#:''this is a little table''
#(''of a sibling'') Younger
#:''this is my little brother''
#trivial
#:''it's of little importance''

====Antonyms====
*[[large]], [[big]]

====Usage note====
*'''Little''' is used with uncountable nouns only. With plural nouns, use [[few]].


